# Test Task

## Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

## Features

- Enter and display text
- Render every character as a separate element
- Ctrl + Click selection
- Rectangle selection
- Drag a single letter
- Drag multiple selected letters
- Swap letters
- Return letters to the output area

## Run

Clone the repository and open `index.html` using Live Server or any local web server.
